   <head>[EPITAPH] ON A NOISY POLEMIC.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Below thir stanes lie Jamie's banes;</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">O Death, it's my opinion,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Thou ne'er took such a bleth'ran b-tch,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Into thy dark dominion!</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
